nt-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">dul </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">dha </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri; mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">nanti </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">tidak akan kekurangan juru-juru sembelih</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri; mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">,â€ tandasnya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri; mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Di sisi lain, Gus Shobih tak lupa menyampaikan harapannya kepada D</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height: 150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">inas </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">P</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">eternakan</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri; mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> dan Kesehatan Hewan Kabupaten Pasruan agar </span><span lang=\"IN\" styl